Program: Omnibus
Title: Disease Detectives
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376lx8
Last Broadcast Date: 23 June 1999
A look at viruses and the search for vaccines and anti-viral drugs. Includes an examination of the efforts to deal with Ebola and to prevent a repeat of the influenza epidemic of 1918. Contributors include William Stone, a 1918 flu pandemic survivor.